    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You knock on a locked or barred object, knocking three times as you will the object to open. Your knock reverberates out, loud and clear, and the object opens.</em></p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><ul><li><p>A target that is held shut by a mundane lock or that is stuck or barred becomes unlocked, unstuck, or unbarred. If the object has multiple locks, only one of them is unlocked.</p></li><li><p>If the target is affected by <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.fsKqUGAIN0YXi4Dm]{arcane lock}</em> the lock is suppressed for 10 minutes.</p></li><li><p>When you cast the spell, a loud knock, audible from as far away as 300 feet, emanates from the target object.</p></li></ul>",
            "chat": "<p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><ul><li><p>A target that is held shut by a mundane lock or that is stuck or barred becomes unlocked, unstuck, or unbarred. If the object has multiple locks, only one of them is unlocked.</p></li><li><p>If the target is affected by <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.fsKqUGAIN0YXi4Dm]{arcane lock}</em> the lock is suppressed for 10 minutes.</p></li><li><p>When you cast the spell, a loud knock, audible from as far away as 300 feet, emanates from the target object.</p></li></ul>"
        },
